plemented on Xilinx Ultrascale+\nFPGAs and supports a throughput of more than 200 Gbps while reducing resource\nusage by almost 10$\\times$ compared to other solutions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Mar 2021 16:58:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-16"}
